===抗老化药物===

目前（2017年），科学家们正在[[模式生物|动物]]的身上研发一些抗衰老的药物。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Childs|first1=Bennett G|last2=Durik|first2=Matej|last3=Baker|first3=Darren J|last4=van Deursen|first4=Jan M|title=Cellular senescence in aging and age-related disease: from mechanisms to therapy|journal=Nature Medicine|date=2015-12-08|volume=21|issue=12|pages=1424–1435|doi=10.1038/nm.4000}}</ref>其中，研究人员观察到{{tsl|en|Calorie restriction|卡路里限制}}（限食）能够延长某些动物的寿命。<ref>{{Cite journal| last2 = Shanmuganayagam| first1 = M. | first2 = D.| last1 = Anderson| title = Caloric restriction and aging: studies in mice and monkeys| last3 = Weindruch | first3 = R.| journal = Toxicologic pathology| volume = 37| issue = 1| pages = 47–51| year = 2009| pmid = 19075044| doi = 10.1177/0192623308329476}}</ref>由此，科学家们试着研发一种称为{{tsl|en|Caloric restriction mimetic|限食拟药}}的药物，来模拟限食带来的生理变化，同时但又不需要人真的去饿肚子。<ref>{{cite web|title=單元二：拒絕老化|url=http://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=newscan&id=1100|publisher=科学人杂志|accessdate=2017-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422033728/http://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?Unit=newscan&id=1100|archive-date=2017-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，科学家还进一步研究了一些被批准作他用的药物。这些药物（包括[[雷帕霉素|雷帕霉素]]<ref name=source25>{{cite journal | year = 2009 | title = Rapamycin fed late in life extends lifespan in genetically heterogeneous mice | journal = Nature | volume = 460 |pages = 392–5 | doi=10.1038/nature08221 | pmid=19587680 | pmc=2786175 | author=Harrison DE, Strong R, Sharp ZD, ''et al.''}}</ref>、[[二甲双胍|二甲双胍]]等多种{{tsl|en|geroprotector|抗衰老剂}}）在服用时可产生和限食类似的生理反应，因此科学家想知道这些药是否也具有延寿的功能。<ref>{{cite journal |year= 2005 | title = Identification of Potential Caloric Restriction Mimetics by Microarray Profiling | journal = Physiological Genomics | volume = 23 | issue = 3| pages = 343–50 | pmid = 16189280 | doi=10.1152/physiolgenomics.00069.2005 | author=Dhahbi JM, Mote PL, Fahy GM, Spindler SR}}</ref>科学家还研究了作为[[营养补充品|营养补充品]]的{{tsl|en|MitoQ}}，[[白藜芦醇|白藜芦醇]]和{{tsl|en|Pterostilbene}}，观察它们是否能以类似的原理令人长寿。<ref name=Kaeberlein>{{cite journal|last=Kaeberlein|first=Matt|title=Resveratrol,pterostilbene and rapamycin:are they anti-aging drugs?|journal=BioEssays|year=2010|volume=32|issue=2|pages=96–99|doi=10.1002/bies.200900171|pmid=20091754}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = A Low Dose of Dietary Resveratrol Partially Mimics Caloric Restriction and Retards Aging Parameters in Mice | journal = PLOS ONE | volume = 3| issue = 6| pages = e2264| doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0002264 | pmid=18523577 | pmc=2386967 | year=2008 | author=Barger JL, Kayo T, Vann JM, ''et al.''}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | pmid = 23691264 | doi=10.1155/2013/575482 | volume=2013 | title=A review of pterostilbene antioxidant activity and disease modification | pmc=3649683 | year=2013 | journal=Oxid Med Cell Longev | page=575482 | author=McCormack D, McFadden D}}</ref>

还有一些其他的抗老化药物顺着另一种思维研发。其中，利用[[端粒酶|端粒酶]]去阻止端粒缩短也是一个很重要的思路。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Telomeres and Telomerase Basic Science Implications for Aging | journal = American Geriatrics Society | volume = 49 | issue = 8| pages = 1105–1109 | doi = 10.1046/j.1532-5415.2001.49217.x }}</ref>然而，这种做法风险不小，因为有些研究表明端粒酶和癌症与肿瘤的形成有关系。<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1158/1541-7786.MCR-05-0147| pmid = 16179494| title = Telomerase and Cancer: Kirk A. Landon - AACR Prize for Basic Cancer Research Lecture| journal = Molecular Cancer Research| volume = 3| issue = 9| pages = 477–82| year = 2005| last1 = Blackburn | first1 = E. H.}}</ref>

